<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">答幻輪法師十疑問并書</cb:mulu>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0777b" n="0777b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="8"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="8"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="8"><cb:jhead>入就瑞白禪師語錄卷之八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b02"/><byline cb:type="editor">明住天台護國寺嗣法門人寂蘊編</byline>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">頌古</cb:mulu><head>頌古</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b04"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b0401" rend="margin-left:2em">世尊陞座。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b05"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b0501">當場一機覿面示伊不假聲色寧屬有為文殊白槌
<lb ed="J" n="0777b06"/>畫鼓聲催昨宵一陣春風起山花處處笑微微。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b07"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b0701" rend="margin-left:2em">拈花。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b0801">拈花示處無多子秪要當機見得親賴有頭陀解微
<lb ed="J" n="0777b09"/>笑直至而今花更新。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b10"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b1001" rend="margin-left:2em">未離兜率<anchor xml:id="beg_6a" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_6a"/>降皇宮未出母胎度人<anchor xml:id="beg_6b" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_6b"/>畢。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b11"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b1101">煦日炤大千明鏡含萬象萬象一光收本無來去相
<lb ed="J" n="0777b12"/>石女唱囉嗹蟭螟吞大象。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b13"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b1301" rend="margin-left:2em">乾闥婆王獻樂迦葉作舞因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b14"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b1401">錦上添花色更鮮婆王自昧作習言長空雲散青天
<lb ed="J" n="0777b15"/>皎五湖波底月團圓。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b1601" rend="margin-left:2em">世尊敕天上人間魔王護法因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b17"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b1701">分明語處露堂堂誰云真佛與魔王不識梅梢春色
<lb ed="J" n="0777b18"/>意空有聲香度粉墻。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b1901" rend="margin-left:2em">圓覺經居一切時不起妄念四句。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b20"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b2001">天明雞報曉日落鳥歸巢雨打階前濕風和花更嬌。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b2101" rend="margin-left:2em">楞嚴經若不見吾不見之地自然非物云何非
<lb ed="J" n="0777b22"/>汝。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b23"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b2301">掃去千崖雪指出老猴精一雙皂子眼徹底放光明
<lb ed="J" n="0777b24"/>噫半夜皂裳休著美天曉牙床不睡強。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b25"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b2501" rend="margin-left:2em">經首<g ref="#CB15315">󳯓</g>字。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b26"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b2601">不是以不成八人人對面如盲瞎開口叫時喚不出
<lb ed="J" n="0777b27"/>仔細思量卻惱殺休惱殺四七元來二十八。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b2801" rend="margin-left:2em">女子出定。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777b29"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777b2901">本無來去何有出入出入元非真來去總成跡文殊
<lb ed="J" n="0777b30"/>與罔明徒廢<anchor xml:id="beg_6c" type="cb-app"/>己<anchor xml:id="end_6c"/>之力燒卻枯椿飛盡灰樵人何處下
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0777c" n="0777c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c01"/>刀劈咄。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c02"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c0201" rend="margin-left:2em"><note place="inline">師室中常以女子出定因緣詰問禪人往往皆作道理會昧卻宗旨故示之以頌</note>。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c03"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c0301">女子文殊罔明拈來勘驗禪人逐境皆因昧<anchor xml:id="beg_6d" type="cb-app"/>己<anchor xml:id="end_6d"/>歸根
<lb ed="J" n="0777c04"/>格外翻身曙色朦朧兮金烏似箭更闌深闇兮玉兔
<lb ed="J" n="0777c05"/>如銀。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c06"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c0601" rend="margin-left:2em"><g ref="#CB06748">𩿶</g>崛摩羅救產難因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c0701">寒泉古澗兮絕波瀾三個鯉魚兮弄影潭山僧看破
<lb ed="J" n="0777c08"/>兮無蹤跡萬古清風兮播宇寰。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c09"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c0901" rend="margin-left:2em"><note place="inline">完初禪人每入室次師以產難因緣詰之惟以道理相酬不能轉身吐氣捩轉向上關師遂以
<lb ed="J" n="0777c10"/>頌示之</note>。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c11"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c1101">石火光中立問端秪要神龍起波瀾神龍不解翻身
<lb ed="J" n="0777c12"/>轉依然死水黑漫漫須領略沒交關莫向言中覓指
<lb ed="J" n="0777c13"/>南春回大地兮山花爛熳秋色澄清兮石骨冰寒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c1401" rend="margin-left:2em">金棺示雙趺。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c1501">四十九年無一字槨示雙趺重舉似大千沙界任流
<lb ed="J" n="0777c16"/>通西風吹起黃花異。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c1701" rend="margin-left:2em">達磨大師對武帝因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c1801">一句全酬截斷咽喉臨鋒寶劍孰敢陳頭朔風彌布
<lb ed="J" n="0777c19"/>兮寒威凜冽六花飄蕩兮冰骨齊周爭柰皇圖劫石
<lb ed="J" n="0777c20"/>固任從風雨御階流。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c21"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c2101">碧眼胡僧早破家梁王殿上撒泥沙龍床穩坐憨憨
<lb ed="J" n="0777c22"/>睡腳踹蘆根意氣賒斷臂安心傳底事而今滿眼數
<lb ed="J" n="0777c23"/>如麻。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c24"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c2401" rend="margin-left:2em">武帝請傅大士講經。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c25"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c2501">大師揮尺涉廉纖那堪更向艸中盤楚王不識連城
<lb ed="J" n="0777c26"/>璧徒使荊人獻聖顏。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c27"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c2701" rend="margin-left:2em">寶公刀尺。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c28"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c2801">主持個事聽從為刀尺杖頭祖意垂利物應機隨處
<lb ed="J" n="0777c29"/>用家私狼藉有誰知。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0777c30"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0777c3001" rend="margin-left:2em">青原不落階級。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0778a" n="0778a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a01"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a0101">撒手捨筌蹄時人那得知菊花三月茂臘月柳花飛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a0201" rend="margin-left:1em">石頭云恁麼也不得不恁麼也不得恁麼不恁麼
<lb ed="J" n="0778a03"/>總不得。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a0401">石壁非泥石甕非攜打破菱花無像可施垂翼大鵬
<lb ed="J" n="0778a05"/>無伴侶陰迷六合達天池。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a06"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a0601" rend="margin-left:1em">馬祖云有時教伊揚眉瞬目有時不教伊<anchor xml:id="beg_6e" type="cb-app"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end_6e"/>眉瞬
<lb ed="J" n="0778a07"/>目有時<anchor xml:id="beg_6f" type="cb-app"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end_6f"/>眉瞬目者是有時<anchor xml:id="beg_70" type="cb-app"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end_70"/>眉瞬目者不是。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a0801">石簣如藏石鷂如翔無可不可南鄉北鄉春蘭秋菊
<lb ed="J" n="0778a09"/>人皆美花下相逄笑一場。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a10"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a1001" rend="margin-left:2em">僧問馬祖離四句絕百非話。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a11"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a1101">崑崗之玉荊山之璧價重連城時流莫識藏頭海頭
<lb ed="J" n="0778a12"/>銀山鐵壁要津把斷無人渡一片銀花黑似漆。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a13"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a1301" rend="margin-left:2em">馬祖日面佛月面佛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a14"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a1401">日面佛月面佛西湖南岸三天竺南高峰對北高峰
<lb ed="J" n="0778a15"/>六條橋鎖垂楊綠。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a1601" rend="margin-left:2em">曹山死貓頭。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a17"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a1701">古巖高掛任風吹雨淋日曝無乾濕若還觸著些兒
<lb ed="J" n="0778a18"/>氣大地眾生腦破裂。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a1901" rend="margin-left:1em">曹山辭洞山山云向甚麼處去荅云不變異處去
<lb ed="J" n="0778a20"/>洞云不變異處豈有去耶曹云去亦不變異。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a2101">碧潭秋夜蟾華映鏡像分明豈動搖識盡髑髏誰賞
<lb ed="J" n="0778a22"/>鑑木人高步出青霄。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a2301" rend="margin-left:2em">南泉斬貓。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a2401">提起劍斬卻貓一段春光人不曉南泉舉似作家兒
<lb ed="J" n="0778a25"/>趙州老人頭戴草頭戴草凜凜威風振華表。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a2601" rend="margin-left:2em">三世諸佛不知有狸奴白牯卻知有。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a2701">王宮深寂寂禁外莫能知一聲哮吼處花葉惹遊絲。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a2801" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈再參馬祖因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778a29"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778a2901">互換之風畫足蛇振威一喝意便賒全提正令全機
<lb ed="J" n="0778a30"/>喪那許時人弄爪牙。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0778b" n="0778b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b01"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b0101" rend="margin-left:2em">僧問百丈如何是奇特事丈云獨坐大雄峰。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b02"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b0201">獨坐大雄峰親言指示儂長空孤月皎幾處色溶溶。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b03"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b0301" rend="margin-left:2em">馬祖送醬百丈因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b0401">馬祖頻陳雄峰全舉一唱一酬師資相許芳草萋萋
<lb ed="J" n="0778b05"/>春光爛熳黃菊離離白帝起舞。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b06"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b0601" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈得大機。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b0701">一喝大鵬擘水開百千龍子盡藏埋玄關三句輕掣
<lb ed="J" n="0778b08"/>斷皮髓何曾得到來。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b0901" rend="margin-left:2em">黃檗得大用。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b1001">一掌擘開華嶽秀源頭流出活水來門風蕩蕩乾坤
<lb ed="J" n="0778b11"/>振普令兒孫紹祖懷。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b12"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b1201" rend="margin-left:2em">黃檗在百丈開田築地因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b1301">師資唱和意非輕打地酬他問地因空裏一聲轟霹
<lb ed="J" n="0778b14"/>靂電光影裏又翻身。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b1501" rend="margin-left:2em">德山托缽。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b1601">明修棧道暗度陳倉巖頭老漢善挈宗綱密啟意別
<lb ed="J" n="0778b17"/>宮商風送清香到洛陽。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b18"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b1801" rend="margin-left:2em">法眼指簾。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b19"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b1901">指簾當處驗渴鹿逐陽焰若能解返擲免被清涼騙。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b2001" rend="margin-left:2em">汝為我開田我為汝說大義因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b2101">大義從來不較多舒開兩手演摩訶片雲歸嶺青山
<lb ed="J" n="0778b22"/>露水面風生六月波。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b2301" rend="margin-left:2em">柏樹子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b2401">柏樹子會也麼一輪明月炤娑婆時人不肯抬頭覷
<lb ed="J" n="0778b25"/>水中撈摸受奔波絕奔波折角泥牛出愛河。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b2601" rend="margin-left:2em">南泉山下有一菴主不禮南泉。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b2701">宮烏棲去玉樓深微月生簷夜夜心香輦不回花自
<lb ed="J" n="0778b28"/>發春來空帶辟寒金。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b2901" rend="margin-left:2em">趙州今夜荅話。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778b30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778b3001">今夜去荅話招啇店裏將旗挂引得啇人進門來奪
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0778c" n="0778c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c01"/>卻財寶遭打罵老趙州老趙州一段冤憎萬古愁。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c0201" rend="margin-left:2em">臺山婆子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c0301">一指路二勘破梅花鏡裏清香墮時人徒自眼糢糊
<lb ed="J" n="0778c04"/>卻向光中尋墮過今日雲門為舉揚雪山六載瞿<note place="inline">曇坐</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c0501" rend="margin-left:2em">麻三斤。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c0601">洞山麻三斤無星秤上稱識取鉤頭意莫認定盤星。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c07"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c0701" rend="margin-left:2em">乾屎橛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c0801">乾屎橛對面說擬思量千里隔一個漆桶向空拋兩
<lb ed="J" n="0778c09"/>個烏龜笑不歇。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c10"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c1001" rend="margin-left:2em">雲門六不收。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c11"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c1101">六不收四時有萬仞峰頭看垂手等閒眨眼過千山
<lb ed="J" n="0778c12"/>瞎驢落在吳塘後花正開柳正舞石女畫眉懶梳洗。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c13"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c1301" rend="margin-left:2em">雲門須彌。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c14"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c1401">須彌山兮覿面提從來不屬有無知牢關打破念情
<lb ed="J" n="0778c15"/>淨赤日蕭蕭任所為。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c1601" rend="margin-left:2em">雲門扇子<g ref="#CB01387">𨁝</g>跳。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c17"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c1701">扇子<g ref="#CB01387">𨁝</g>跳拄杖解笑拂子高飛禪板嘶鬧雲門老漢
<lb ed="J" n="0778c18"/>總不知三世諸佛曾未到。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c1901" rend="margin-left:2em">雲門一字關。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c20"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c2001">普響新露確電光難湊泊遇著雪公子一串都穿卻
<lb ed="J" n="0778c21"/>錯天下衲子徒描摸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c22"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c2201" rend="margin-left:2em">雲門餅。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c23"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c2301">橘赤橙黃桃紅柳綠現前三昧時人不復堪<anchor xml:id="beg_71" type="cb-app"/>羨<anchor xml:id="end_71"/>雲門
<lb ed="J" n="0778c24"/>老古錐問著只將胡餅<g ref="#CB05218">𡎺</g>咄明眼衲僧莫輕忽。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c25"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c2501" rend="margin-left:2em">南山起雲北山下雨。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c26"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c2601">南山起雲北山雨無陰陽地花飛舞折腳波斯摘一
<lb ed="J" n="0778c27"/>枝清香飄入鄰家去。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c2801" rend="margin-left:2em">仰山指雪獅子話。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0778c29"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0778c2901">雪獅子指示人不解翻身平地沉賴有雲門傍著眼
<lb ed="J" n="0778c30"/>轉躬推倒楚王城和風起煦日臨超然一色化乾坤
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0779a" n="0779a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a01"/>柳垂煙岸添新色上苑花開布錦屏。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a0201" rend="margin-left:2em">板齒生毛語。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a0301">何曾祖意有西來板齒生毛若話陪雪覆千山人影
<lb ed="J" n="0779a04"/>絕夜深撥棹古灣回。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a0501" rend="margin-left:2em">投子荅趙州不許夜行投明須到。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a0601">不許夜行投明到玉石鑄成生鐵銚木童拿去煎餈
<lb ed="J" n="0779a07"/>糕石女看來呵呵笑。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a08"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a0801" rend="margin-left:2em">趙州茶。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a0901">遙想當年趙州老逄人秪獻一甌茶如能當下親承
<lb ed="J" n="0779a10"/>得明月清風意自賒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a1101" rend="margin-left:2em">丹霞燒木佛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a1201" rend="margin-left:1em">丹霞燒木佛火燄為三世諸佛說法院主眉鬚墮
<lb ed="J" n="0779a13"/>落穿卻祖師鼻孔天下禪和穿鑿料掉沒交涉且
<lb ed="J" n="0779a14"/>看老瑞如何頌出。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a15"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a1501">木佛燒來顯大機眉鬚墮落又相為要知個裏端的
<lb ed="J" n="0779a16"/>意秋林黃葉逐風飛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a1701" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈野狐。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a1801">不落不昧露堂堂五百生狐絕覆藏杖頭挑出明舉
<lb ed="J" n="0779a19"/>似方知異類放毫光。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a2001" rend="margin-left:2em">黃龍三關。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a2101">我手何似佛手南北烏飛兔走我腳何似驢蹄石女
<lb ed="J" n="0779a22"/>踢翻須彌人人盡有生緣五虎曾下西川<note place="inline">咦</note>一枝梅
<lb ed="J" n="0779a23"/>破臘幾處草芽鮮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a24"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a2401" rend="margin-left:2em">大蘿蔔頭。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a25"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a2501">趙州拈出大蘿蔔塞斷天下衲僧口千古萬古硬紏
<lb ed="J" n="0779a26"/>紏黃頭碧眼難下手忽下手銅兒倒騎鐵馬走。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a27"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a2701" rend="margin-left:2em">日日是好日。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a28"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a2801">日日是好日元旦即初一春至百花開秋來樹頭赤。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a2901" rend="margin-left:2em">婆子三十年供養個死漢。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779a30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779a3001">枯木寒崖髑髏遍地湛水澄潭睡龍藏聚浪裏翻身
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0779b" n="0779b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b01"/>世間有幾一條白練鎖虛空明暗雙雙何忌諱。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b0201" rend="margin-left:2em">風穴一塵。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b0301">明暗繇來顯妙傳掃除明暗若為觀日頭夜半昇峰
<lb ed="J" n="0779b04"/>頂瑞草無根色更鮮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b0501" rend="margin-left:2em">僧問大隨一字壞。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b0601">大隨一字壞匝地清風撲面蓋常流衲子眼未開千
<lb ed="J" n="0779b07"/>里迢迢還路債投子忒煞老婆心猶自裝香遙禮拜
<lb ed="J" n="0779b08"/>遙禮拜露古熊一陣微雨灑東林滿地落花真可愛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b0901" rend="margin-left:2em">僧問大隨如何是室中燈隨云三人證龜成鱉。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b1001">句中無味若為參禪者徒勞話歲寒焰焰祖燈明歷
<lb ed="J" n="0779b11"/>歷朔風吹處嶺雲寒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b12"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b1201" rend="margin-left:2em">草鞋覆龜。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b1301">一個烏龜覿面提何須更問祖師機草鞋蓋覆重拈
<lb ed="J" n="0779b14"/>出雨滴簷頭地有泥。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b1501" rend="margin-left:2em">玄沙膿滴滴。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b1601">膿滴滴君難識紅如硃黑似漆玄沙惡氣遍天下至
<lb ed="J" n="0779b17"/>今聞者頭腦裂。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b18"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b1801" rend="margin-left:2em">玄沙天龍見虎話。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b19"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b1901">是虎是汝兩俱錯雪竇更添一落索石人半夜睡正
<lb ed="J" n="0779b20"/>濃此時誰能下註腳不註腳桃花綻去春風惡。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b2101" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問巴陵如何是吹毛劍陵云珊瑚枝枝撐著月。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b22"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b2201">吹毛覿面提珊瑚當處絕嬌花不帶春秪要應時節
<lb ed="J" n="0779b23"/>別別秤鎚陀上三斤鐵。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b24"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b2401" rend="margin-left:2em">巴陵祖意教意。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b25"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b2501">雞上樹鴨下水好個鐵蒺藜虧了巴陵使來年七月
<lb ed="J" n="0779b26"/>中秋風又復起。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b27"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b2701" rend="margin-left:2em">高峰無夢無想主人公。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b28"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b2801">打碎琉璃碗卸卻珍御服枕子開口笑雙髻罵天目。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b2901" rend="margin-left:2em">欽山一鏃破三關。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779b30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779b3001">一鏃破三關晡時夜未闌與君放出關中主煤人頭
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0779c" n="0779c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c01"/>戴鐵帽舞碧眼胡僧尚不知釋迦彌勒目雙瞽。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c0201" rend="margin-left:2em">白水聲色。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c0301">借來聊爾了門頭豈把芒繩繫死牛玉鼠銀盆雖類
<lb ed="J" n="0779c04"/>色到頭不許一般收。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c0501" rend="margin-left:1em">五祖演云如牛過窗櫺頭角四蹄都過了秪有尾
<lb ed="J" n="0779c06"/>巴過不得。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c0701">功齊功化何曾了<anchor xml:id="beg_72" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_72"/>到家鄉未徹頭直須翻轉乾坤
<lb ed="J" n="0779c08"/>也楊子江心水倒流。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c0901" rend="margin-left:1em">圓悟問大慧云踞虎頭收虎尾第一句下明宗旨
<lb ed="J" n="0779c10"/>如何是第一句慧云此是第二句。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c11"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c1101">抹殺人滅卻法第一句中阿喇喇獅子翻身入母群
<lb ed="J" n="0779c12"/>免墮寒巖青草下。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c13"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c1301" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問審哲禪師如何是佛法大意哲曰貧兒抱子
<lb ed="J" n="0779c14"/>渡恩愛兢隨波。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c1501">薰風渡汨羅綠水湧清波遍界雲影動涉躐盡偏頗。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c1601" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問雲居簡孤峰獨宿時如何簡曰九間僧堂不
<lb ed="J" n="0779c17"/>宿誰教你獨宿孤峰。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c1801">夜深石女臥眠床天曉木人忙喚起池上鴛鴦獨自
<lb ed="J" n="0779c19"/>鳴一聲飛入紅蓼裏。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c2001" rend="margin-left:2em">香嚴上樹。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c2101">樹上樹下最威雄鐵額銅頭怎觸鋒雲散長空孤月
<lb ed="J" n="0779c22"/>淨天柱卻在萬雲中。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c2301" rend="margin-left:2em">疏山造塔。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c2401">一文錢折角泥牛海底眠二文錢石女梳粧出庭前
<lb ed="J" n="0779c25"/>三文錢柳綠桃紅三月天九斤龜毛長三丈臘月蓮
<lb ed="J" n="0779c26"/>花色更鮮尋聲逐色兮徒勞側耳返本還源兮鼻孔
<lb ed="J" n="0779c27"/>遼天。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c2801" rend="margin-left:2em">貓兒偏愛捉老鼠。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0779c29"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0779c2901">朝悠悠暮悠悠金風匝地冷愀愀天皇皇地皇皇三
<lb ed="J" n="0779c30"/>春柳絮白如霜化母造成無功錦那許傍人話短長。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0780a" n="0780a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a01"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a0101" rend="margin-left:1em">疏山問溈山有句無句如藤倚樹樹倒藤枯句歸
<lb ed="J" n="0780a02"/>何處溈山呵呵大笑歸方丈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a0301">東京掃蕩西京滅一統山河歸至尊笑罷不知何處
<lb ed="J" n="0780a04"/>去霜天月夜子規鳴。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a0501" rend="margin-left:2em">婆子請趙州轉藏。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a0601">一匝旋來大地收任他諸佛莫能酬縱饒婆子解機
<lb ed="J" n="0780a07"/>變也是人前強出頭。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a08"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a0801" rend="margin-left:2em">仰山插<anchor xml:id="beg_73" type="cb-app"/>鍬<anchor xml:id="end_73"/>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a0901">父子相逄事便奇插下<anchor xml:id="beg_74" type="cb-app"/>鍬<anchor xml:id="end_74"/>時<anchor xml:id="beg_75" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_75"/>露機南山刈茅人大
<lb ed="J" n="0780a10"/>有宗風從此振華夷。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a1101" rend="margin-left:1em">熊秀才乘藍輿至西山偶見一僧貌古神清龐眉
<lb ed="J" n="0780a12"/>雪頂葉衣坐於磐石才下輿問曰莫是亮座主麼
<lb ed="J" n="0780a13"/>老僧以手向東一指才隨手東視回觀老僧不見。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a14"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a1401">一指當陽舉似人韓盧逐塊枉勞神若向東方空看
<lb ed="J" n="0780a15"/>指回頭昧卻本來真。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a1601" rend="margin-left:1em">秀才嘆曰夙緣不厚雖遇而不遇也。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a17"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a1701">雖遇而不遇甕中不走鱉再上藍輿時虛空吞皎月。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a18"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0780a1801">香嚴獨腳頌兼著語</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a1901" rend="margin-left:1em">子啐母啄<note place="inline">動也動也</note>子覺母殼<note place="inline">轉位就功即不無怎奈拋家散走</note>子母
<lb ed="J" n="0780a20"/>俱亡<note place="inline">那畔今時一齊歸</note>應緣不錯<note place="inline">物物全彰頭頭合轍</note>同道唱和<note place="inline">月印
<lb ed="J" n="0780a21"/>寒潭</note>方名獨腳<note place="inline">惟我獨尊</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a22"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a2201">子母從來不二途子纔觸處母同遊孩兒若得身榮
<lb ed="J" n="0780a23"/>貴脫卻老娘舊住樓子母如能俱亡也九月楊花遍
<lb ed="J" n="0780a24"/>地周柳林黃鵲穿梭舞那有青紅染指頭。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a25"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a2501" rend="margin-left:2em">染深水牯牛<note place="inline">有僧從金粟來說金栗有染深水牯牛話請師荅語更請頌之</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a26"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a2601">天明放去離欄圈烈性猖狂舞似風煩惱海中雙足
<lb ed="J" n="0780a27"/>涉無明林裏一身沖東西兩岸貪苗稼四棄三途露
<lb ed="J" n="0780a28"/>影蹤忽地拽來驀鼻看依然還是這牛兒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a2901" rend="margin-left:2em">事事無礙。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780a30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780a3001">事事無礙非中非外打破虛空銷鎔法界石女騰空
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0780b" n="0780b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b01"/>鐵船裝載火裏蟭螟現神作怪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b02"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0780b0201">頌雲棲大師公案一則</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b03"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b0301" rend="margin-left:1em">黃侍郎問師云夜來老鼠唧唧說盡一部華嚴經
<lb ed="J" n="0780b04"/>大師云貓兒突出時如何黃無對大師代云走卻
<lb ed="J" n="0780b05"/>法師留下講案。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b0601">華嚴歷歷談非舌聞者應須著眼參突出烏花白貓
<lb ed="J" n="0780b07"/>子管教一吼髑髏乾雲棲老幾多般法師走卻兮雲
<lb ed="J" n="0780b08"/>封古岫留下講案兮霧鎖寒潭。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b09"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0780b0901">頌雲門顯聖先和尚公案十三則</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b10"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b1001" rend="margin-left:1em">神珠問某甲不恁麼問時如何師曰戲論珠云恁
<lb ed="J" n="0780b11"/>麼問時如何師曰戲論珠云恁麼不恁麼總不問
<lb ed="J" n="0780b12"/>時如何師曰戲論珠云還有向上事也無師曰有
<lb ed="J" n="0780b13"/>珠云如何是向上事師曰戲論。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b14"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b1401">本入龍宮探驪珠覿面拈來一物無不是龍王多把
<lb ed="J" n="0780b15"/>住恐教大地別親疏。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b1601" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問祖師禪如來禪是同是別師曰古越是杭州
<lb ed="J" n="0780b17"/>曰恁麼則同也師曰長江分彼此。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b1801">古越是杭州長江分彼此若知絃外音揚聲囉囉哩。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b1901" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問如何是圓相師曰大燒餅。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b20"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b2001">燒餅托出任君飧底意繇來非等閑不是仰山親嫡
<lb ed="J" n="0780b21"/>子何能特地示毫端須領略莫顢頇春風蕩漾兮花
<lb ed="J" n="0780b22"/>開碧岫秋色臨空兮霧起寒巖。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b2301" rend="margin-left:1em">師同陶石簣無念師向火石簣曰無念師在此阿
<lb ed="J" n="0780b24"/>師得力句乞為舉似師曰向火背猶寒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b25"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b2501">六月日頭炎似火三冬朔氣冷如冰一句當陽無縫
<lb ed="J" n="0780b26"/>罅不落言思始可親。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b27"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b2701" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問如何是暗機師曰凌霄峰。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b28"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b2801">凌霄峰莫朦朧摩尼寶珠映現無窮識取珠體莫認
<lb ed="J" n="0780b29"/>青紅金風黃葉秋林落幾家砧杵月明中。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780b30"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780b3001" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問如何是義海師曰半山亭。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0780c" n="0780c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c01"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c0101">胸中無得失舌底是非空一輪明月皓幾處色朦朧。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c0201" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問如何是生死中不生死的道理師曰舌頭短
<lb ed="J" n="0780c03"/>三寸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c0401">三寸舌頭短衲僧巴鼻長秋風吹桂萼遍界盡馨香。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c0501" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問十方薄伽梵一路涅槃門乞師指個路頭師
<lb ed="J" n="0780c06"/>曰那個是御愛峰。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c0701">水流東徑朝西徑雲起南峰過北峰舉似分明無別
<lb ed="J" n="0780c08"/>旨涅槃頭路翠叢叢。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c0901" rend="margin-left:1em">和尚一日喫茶次拈果子云法身遍滿一切處若
<lb ed="J" n="0780c10"/>道這個果子具法身恁麼則喫卻法身若道不具
<lb ed="J" n="0780c11"/>則法身有不遍之處汝等諸人揀點看看。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c1201">是法身非法身兩重枷鎖難為情透網金鱗擺尾去
<lb ed="J" n="0780c13"/>豈向鉤頭把餌吞徑山老休顢人泥童翫月消情緒
<lb ed="J" n="0780c14"/>木馬嘶風俊不禁。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c1501" rend="margin-left:1em">和尚一日舉雲棲大師云我聞雲棲和尚滅度後
<lb ed="J" n="0780c16"/>有人於庫房中見若他道生西方為甚麼又在庫
<lb ed="J" n="0780c17"/>房中既在庫房中有違西方願力汝等諸人試定
<lb ed="J" n="0780c18"/>當看。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c19"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c1901">脫體無依絕去來徑山和尚強安排沒絃琴韻人難
<lb ed="J" n="0780c20"/>委獨坐朝陽空抱腮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c2101" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問和尚曰乞和尚指示心要出離生死真實的
<lb ed="J" n="0780c22"/>意和尚曰我從來無一字與人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c23"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c2301">鐵甲將軍塞外威痴心只要討皇基鉗鎚擊碎黃金
<lb ed="J" n="0780c24"/>骨脫卻龍袍卸甲歸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c25"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c2501" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問和尚曰和尚在此作甚麼師云殺人僧云只
<lb ed="J" n="0780c26"/>恐和尚不會殺師便掌。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c2701">眼蓋乾坤意氣高吹毛倒握驗英豪可憐不解知機
<lb ed="J" n="0780c28"/>變徒把殘軀一旦拋。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0780c29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0780c2901" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問四大分散後向何處安身立命師曰你問這
<lb ed="J" n="0780c30"/>樣大法也不禮三拜僧禮拜師呵呵大笑。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0781a" n="0781a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a01"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a0101">急水灘頭著一篙惹得驪龍鼓浪濤萬斛之舟俱覆
<lb ed="J" n="0781a02"/>卻篙師猶執手中橈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a03"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0781a0301">頌金粟密雲禪師十則</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a04"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a0401" rend="margin-left:1em">粟顧漢月舉僧問古德云朗月當空時如何古德
<lb ed="J" n="0781a05"/>云猶是階下漢僧云請師接上階古德云月落後
<lb ed="J" n="0781a06"/>來相見既是月落後且道如何相見月便出法堂
<lb ed="J" n="0781a07"/>粟下座。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a0801">海枯水竭須彌倒黃頭碧眼一齊掃下座出堂端的
<lb ed="J" n="0781a09"/>意金毛獅子不落草。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a10"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a1001" rend="margin-left:1em">漢月問海眾雲從慈霖天澍現躍飛騰則不問如
<lb ed="J" n="0781a11"/>何是驅雷掣電底句粟便喝進云恁麼則金粟花
<lb ed="J" n="0781a12"/>開寶林果熟去也粟又喝月禮拜歸眾。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a1301">一喝須教作者知更加一喝大慈悲雙收雙放明宗
<lb ed="J" n="0781a14"/>旨不忮不求世所稀風磨鐵壁猶如洗雨灑殘紅襯
<lb ed="J" n="0781a15"/>馬蹄。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a1601" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問狹路相逢髑髏粉碎當恁麼時無位真人在
<lb ed="J" n="0781a17"/>何處安身立命粟云天上天下惟我獨尊僧云恁
<lb ed="J" n="0781a18"/>麼則萬里無雲一輪迥炤去也粟云腳跟下好與
<lb ed="J" n="0781a19"/>三十棒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a20"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a2001">三尺短一尺長個中元不帶商量萬里無雲一輪炤
<lb ed="J" n="0781a21"/>腳跟紅線絆千行三十棒斷愁腸掃除凡聖提挈宗
<lb ed="J" n="0781a22"/>綱山花發笑兮春迴大地籬菊開殘兮冬有嚴霜。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a2301" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問曹溪一滴直透龍池曹溪一滴即不問如何
<lb ed="J" n="0781a24"/>直透龍池底事粟云穿過髑髏進云源遠流長一
<lb ed="J" n="0781a25"/>句作麼生道粟云但與麼去僧便禮拜。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a26"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a2601">直透龍池伸一問廣慧波濤如海闊金粟門頭不見
<lb ed="J" n="0781a27"/>人大地山河俱覆卻與麼去真灑落不立聖凡烏有
<lb ed="J" n="0781a28"/>圭角蓬萊高閣兮越州聖境煙雨樓臺兮福城清樂。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781a29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781a2901" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問如何是金粟境粟云四野桑田進云如何是
<lb ed="J" n="0781a30"/>境中人粟云金粟峰頭望僧云人境<anchor xml:id="beg_76" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_76"/>蒙師指示
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0781b" n="0781b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b01"/>擊鼓陞堂事若何粟云瞻之仰之。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b02"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b0201">四野桑田不是境峰頭望底亦非人當陽拈出無迴
<lb ed="J" n="0781b03"/>互瞻之仰之覿面陳電光石火兮拿雲攫霧慈霖普
<lb ed="J" n="0781b04"/>澍兮廣濟眾生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b0501" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問聲色未萌睹聞莫及正恁麼時乞和尚通個
<lb ed="J" n="0781b06"/>消息粟默然良久乃震威一喝僧云人間四月春
<lb ed="J" n="0781b07"/>光盡金粟秋來菊正開長恨春歸無覓處誰知轉
<lb ed="J" n="0781b08"/>入此中來師云葛藤窠裏藏頭縮尾。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b0901">踢倒蕊香幢須彌山粉碎毘盧不現境乾坤無一事
<lb ed="J" n="0781b10"/>金藏雲起世間成界立娑婆分四至。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b1101" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問如何是佛法的的大意粟便打僧云猶是古
<lb ed="J" n="0781b12"/>時家風粟復打云汝作古時家風會。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b1301">咄活潑潑轉轆轆覿面全提無榮無辱一段靈光絕
<lb ed="J" n="0781b14"/>古今何須特地生疑惑。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b1501" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問如何是本來面目粟云舌頭拖地。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b1601">眼觀山色秀耳聽水聲悠舌頭拖地處特地為君酬。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b1701" rend="margin-left:1em">金粟示眾云突出難辨坐斷千差萬別一塵舉起
<lb ed="J" n="0781b18"/>透徹萬別千差。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b19"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b1901">沒蹤跡斷消息上下四維銀山鐵壁機思盡淨絕塵
<lb ed="J" n="0781b20"/>埃一個銕鎚空裏擲空裏擲船高水長雨落地濕。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b2101" rend="margin-left:2em">拄杖子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b22"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b2201">稜稜角角閃閃爍爍炤用齊行殺活縱奪棒起臨濟
<lb ed="J" n="0781b23"/>正宗扶持楊岐驢腳虛空攪得成團大地撒為塵末
<lb ed="J" n="0781b24"/><note place="inline">咦</note>分明指示諸君也惟有桐溪最清徹。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b25"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b2501" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問倪禪師如何是石門境倪云猿啼獅子崖前
<lb ed="J" n="0781b26"/>石龍吼文殊寺裏鐘。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b2701">一聲漁笛破滄浪幾點桃花映水紅清興一團何所
<lb ed="J" n="0781b28"/>有遊人空自對東風。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781b29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781b2901" rend="margin-left:1em">又問如何是境中人倪云踏破虎溪橋下月坐斷
<lb ed="J" n="0781b30"/>天池第一峰。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0781c" n="0781c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c01"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c0101">世界清平宇宙寬得盤桓處且盤桓東山石女三分
<lb ed="J" n="0781c02"/>話西海泥童話幾般。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c03"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c0301" rend="margin-left:2em">總。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c0401">輝煌燈火元宵夜燦爛星河霽碧時覿面相陳無剩
<lb ed="J" n="0781c05"/>語徒教人境話支離。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c06"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0781c0601">大陽三句</p><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c0605" rend="margin-left:2em;inline">平常無生句。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c0701">乍起和風柳眼青頭頭善應妙難尋空中鳥跡水中
<lb ed="J" n="0781c08"/>影碓嘴生花色更新。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c0901" rend="margin-left:2em">玄妙無私句。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c1001">棒喝交馳任意遊金針玉線縫皆周弘通妙挾無遺
<lb ed="J" n="0781c11"/>影法界塵毛兩俱收。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c12"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c1201" rend="margin-left:2em">體妙無盡句。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0781c1301">一顆摩尼觸處彰施為盡是白毫光古今爍破曾無
<lb ed="J" n="0781c14"/>間涉水登山任舉揚。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0781c15"/>
